### Flow 1: Q&A - product question
POST {{host}}/chat
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "message": "Tell me about laptops, what do you have?",
  "session_id": "qa-demo"
}

### Flow 1: Q&A - follow-up, same session
POST {{host}}/chat
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "message": "Do you have any wireless headphones?",
  "session_id": "qa-demo"
}

### Flow 1b: Semantic RAG - no keyword overlap (expects: UltraBook 13 Air)
# "lightweight to carry while traveling" -> matches "ultraportable / lightweight",
# even though the query never says "laptop". Keyword search would miss this.
POST {{host}}/chat
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "message": "I need something really light to carry around while traveling",
  "session_id": "rag-demo"
}

### Flow 1b: Semantic RAG - intent, not keywords (expects: SlatePad Pro 11)
# "take notes and sketch by hand" -> matches stylus support / drawing / note-taking.
POST {{host}}/chat
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "message": "What can I use to take notes and sketch by hand?",
  "session_id": "rag-demo"
}

### Flow 1b: Semantic RAG - paraphrase (expects: Rugged Phone Go)
# "survives being dropped in water" -> matches "water and dust resistant / IP68".
POST {{host}}/chat
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "message": "Which phone survives being dropped in water?",
  "session_id": "rag-demo"
}

### Flow 1b: Semantic RAG - use case (expects: PulseFit Watch)
# "track my running and heart rate" -> matches fitness smartwatch / GPS / heart rate.
POST {{host}}/chat
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "message": "I want to track my running and heart rate",
  "session_id": "rag-demo"
}

### Flow 1b: Semantic RAG - problem statement (expects: AeroStand Aluminum)
# "back hurts at my desk" -> matches "improves posture", zero shared keywords.
POST {{host}}/chat
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "message": "My back hurts when I work at my desk all day, any ideas?",
  "session_id": "rag-demo"
}

### Flow 2: Order - HITL step 1: draft
POST {{host}}/chat
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "message": "I want to buy a ProBook 15",
  "session_id": "order-demo"
}

### Flow 2: Order - HITL step 2: confirm
POST {{host}}/chat
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "message": "yes",
  "session_id": "order-demo"
}

### Flow 2 (variant): Order - HITL step 1: draft
POST {{host}}/chat
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "message": "I want to buy BudgetPhone X",
  "session_id": "order-cancel-demo"
}

### Flow 2 (variant): Order - HITL step 2: cancel
POST {{host}}/chat
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "message": "no",
  "session_id": "order-cancel-demo"
}

### Guardrail: off-topic - should be rejected
POST {{host}}/chat
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "message": "What's the weather like today?",
  "session_id": "guard-demo"
}

### Guardrail: empty message - Pydantic 422
POST {{host}}/chat
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "message": "",
  "session_id": "guard-demo"
}

